    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 5 (Spell Level 3)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 19 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 7 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 20</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You shape your Chakra, sending it to a creature you have been bonded to by the Fuinjutsu: Ninjou Kan technique in order to strengthen it. The bonded creature gains a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls or a +1 dodge bonus to Defense and Reflex saves,. You can double the bonus by increasing the technique's cost to 4.<br><br>A creature cannot be affected by this technique more than once at the same time.</p>\n\n\n\n",
